items.title: Westgate’s free Touchdown Tailgate is back for football season
items.summary:
Football fans who are in-the-know make their way to Westgate Entertainment District before every Arizona Cardinals home game for the popular Touchdown Tailgate that attracts thousands of fans looking to party and represent their allegiances before kickoff.
